le/.premium/idf-investigation-reveals-high-probability-that-hostage-killed-during-air-force-bombing/0000018d-8e4d-d9cc-a5cd-ffffe7840000</guid></item><item><title>战时以色列的愤怒正在上升，以色列人必须去战斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/anger-is-rising-in-wartime-israel-about-which-israelis-must-go-and-fight/0000018d-89a7-d9cc-a5cd-fdbf2eb20000</link><description>自加沙战争开始以来，许多预备役军人已经穿了四个月的军装，以色列的极端正统派和世俗社区正在就谁必须在以色列国防军服役的问题发生冲突。总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡已经在努力集结军队</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 14:33:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/anger-is-rising-in-wartime-israel-about-which-israelis-must-go-and-fight/0000018d-89a7-d9cc-a5cd-fdbf2eb20000</guid></item><item><title>联合国表示，加沙近 10% 的五岁以下儿童现在严重营养不良</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/almost-10-percent-of-gazas-under-fives-now-acutely-malnourished-un-says/0000018d-8e04-d1e0-a3ff-9ffff73a0000</link><description>由于食品卡车经常遭到饥饿人群的围攻，救援人员报告说，儿童有明显的饥饿迹象，特别是在加沙北部和中部地区</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 13:57:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/almost-10-percent-of-gazas-under-fives-now-acutely-malnourished-un-says/0000018d-8e04-d1e0-a3ff-9ffff73a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列空袭加沙拉法，美国警告不要在该市进行地面行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/israeli-airstrikes-hit-gazas-rafah-as-u-s-warns-against-ground-operation-in-city/0000018d-8d83-d9cc-a5cd-fdbb03d70000</link><description>夜间空袭造成 22 人死亡，袭击了拉法的两栋住宅楼，并损坏了一座由幼儿园改建的流离失所巴勒斯坦人避难所</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 11:47:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/israeli-airstrikes-hit-gazas-rafah-as-u-s-warns-against-ground-operation-in-city/0000018d-8d83-d9cc-a5cd-fdbb03d70000</guid></item><item><title>拜登称以色列在加沙的反应“过度”，寻求暂停战斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/biden-israeli-military-conduct-in-gaza-over-the-top-working-for-sustained-pause/0000018d-8c88-d5e7-ad8d-efa867620000</link><description>拜登表示，他一直与卡塔尔、埃及和沙特阿拉伯领导人保持联系，以使最大程度的人道主义援助进入加沙。总统补充说，“有很多无辜的人正在挨饿、陷入困境和死亡”。 “它必须停止”</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 06:42:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/biden-israeli-military-conduct-in-gaza-over-the-top-working-for-sustained-pause/0000018d-8c88-d5e7-ad8d-efa867620000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡向以色列人发出明确信息：放弃人质符合国家利益</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-clear-message-to-israelis-abandoning-the-hostages-is-in-the-national-interest/0000018d-8a8b-d443-a19f-fe9baf840000</link><description>总理“全面胜利”口号的潜台词是，以人质换取停火协议将阻止以色列国防军完成任务。 与此同时，领土政府活动协调员正准备重新实施戒严令关于加沙</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 04:00:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-clear-message-to-israelis-abandoning-the-hostages-is-in-the-national-interest/0000018d-8a8b-d443-a19f-fe9baf840000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯的协议尚未结束，即使内塔尼亚胡另有说法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/the-israel-hamas-deal-is-not-dead-yet-even-if-netanyahu-says-otherwise/0000018d-898c-d9cc-a5cd-fdbe698c0000</link><description>与总理给人的印象相反，哈马斯的回答似乎为达成协议留下了回旋余地。 ■ 战争期间的战术成就并不能保证以色列取得“全面”战略胜利。 ■ 服务负担正在扩大，但并没有增加。对于极端正统派</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 04:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/the-israel-hamas-deal-is-not-dead-yet-even-if-netanyahu-says-otherwise/0000018d-898c-d9cc-a5cd-fdbe698c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡命令以色列军队提出撤离拉法平民、击败哈马斯的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article-live/biden-says-israeli-military-conduct-in-gaza-is-over-the-top-pushing-for-pause/0000018d-8be5-d5e7-ad8d-ebe5fc430000</link><description>总理内塔尼亚胡要求以色列国防军制定双重计划，从拉法撤离平民并击败哈马斯部队 ■ 从黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射反坦克导弹，以色列空军发起报复性打击 ■ 叙利亚称在大马士革附近击落了两架无人机 ■ 匈牙利、捷克共和国沉没欧盟努力对暴力的以色列定居者实施制裁</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 03:30:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article-live/biden-says-israeli-military-conduct-in-gaza-is-over-the-top-pushing-for-pause/0000018d-8be5-d5e7-ad8d-ebe5fc430000</guid></item><item><title>“我一生都住在以色列。很难接受我儿子要保释”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-02-09/ty-article/.highlight/i-lived-my-whole-life-in-israel-its-hard-to-accept-that-my-son-is-bailing/0000018d-8b33-d5e7-ad8d-ebb3093c0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一对父子努力应对后者离开以色列的决定</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 00:36:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-02-09/ty-article/.highlight/i-lived-my-whole-life-in-israel-its-hard-to-accept-that-my-son-is-bailing/0000018d-8b33-d5e7-ad8d-ebb3093c0000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列当权者正在武装他们的支持者。政治影响是深远的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/people-in-power-in-israel-are-arming-supporters-the-political-implications-are-profound/0000018d-8ade-d5e7-ad8d-ebfe637e0000</link><description>他曾经将以色列视为安全使用枪支的典范。现在，美国枪支政策专家警告以色列正在犯与美国相同的错误</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 00:08:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/people-in-power-in-israel-are-arming-supporters-the-political-implications-are-profound/0000018d-8ade-d5e7-ad8d-ebfe637e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的生育率正在进入一个引人注目的新时代</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israels-fertility-rate-is-entering-a-dramatic-new-era/0000018d-8a6b-d9cc-a5cd-fffb664b0000</link><description>以色列各族群中的女性生育的孩子越来越少。世俗社会正危险地徘徊在所谓的更替水平附近，此时他们的数量开始萎缩</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 22:36:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israels-fertility-rate-is-entering-a-dramatic-new-era/0000018d-8a6b-d9cc-a5cd-fffb664b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战时内阁讨论哈马斯停火提议，抗议人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/protests-held-for-against-hostage-deal-as-war-cabinet-discusses-hamas-proposal/0000018d-8a7a-d9cc-a5cd-fffa554c0000</link><description>数千人在耶路撒冷的以色列政府大院外示威反对释放人质协议，而在特拉维夫，人质的家人及其支持者则抗议支持协议</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 21:41:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/protests-held-for-against-hostage-deal-as-war-cabinet-discusses-hamas-proposal/0000018d-8a7a-d9cc-a5cd-fffa554c0000</guid></item><item><title>延长以色列兵役期限的法案因豁免正统派而引起愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/bill-extending-israeli-army-service-draws-ire-for-exempting-haredim/0000018d-8a40-d443-a19f-fed132dc0000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，该计划旨在满足10月7日事件以及加沙地带战争后果后的军队建设需求，但没有提及征召极端正统派人员的问题</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 20:34:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/bill-extending-israeli-army-service-draws-ire-for-exempting-haredim/0000018d-8a40-d443-a19f-fed132dc0000</guid></item><item><title>当动物饲料制成的皮塔饼是您最好的情况时：加沙地带北部的生活</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/when-pita-made-of-animal-feed-is-your-best-case-scenario-life-in-northern-gaza/0000018d-89f5-d5e7-ad8d-ebf59baf0000</link><description>没有香烟、电或饮用水；一罐金枪鱼售价 100 谢克尔，但 ATM 机被关闭：加沙地带北部局势快照</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 20:29:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/when-pita-made-of-animal-feed-is-your-best-case-scenario-life-in-northern-gaza/0000018d-89f5-d5e7-ad8d-ebf59baf0000</guid></item><item><title>由于以色列不承诺停止援助抗议活动，布林肯取消了加沙过境访问</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/blinken-cancels-gaza-crossing-visit-after-israel-doesnt-commit-to-stopping-aid-protests/0000018d-8a38-d443-a19f-feb9d3010000</link><description>美国国务卿本应亲自评估援助卡车从以色列前往加沙的通道，但由于担心抗议者出现，阻止援助卡车进入加沙，访问被取消</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 20:19:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/blinken-cancels-gaza-crossing-visit-after-israel-doesnt-commit-to-stopping-aid-protests/0000018d-8a38-d443-a19f-feb9d3010000</guid></item><item><title>由于航班将返回以色列，英国航空公司最大限度地减少了运营、飞机和机组人员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/british-airways-minimizes-operations-plane-and-crew-as-flights-set-to-return-to-israel/0000018d-89be-d5e7-ad8d-ebbe48dc0000</link><description>在飞往以色列的途中，这架飞机将在塞浦路斯停留 45 分钟，进行机组人员换班，而乘客则留在机上。由于保险公司的条件，船员不会在以色列过夜</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 20:09:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/british-airways-minimizes-operations-plane-and-crew-as-flights-set-to-return-to-israel/0000018d-89be-d5e7-ad8d-ebbe48dc0000</guid></item><item><title>“无处可归”：《国土报》如何讲述加沙被毁的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-08/ty-article/.highlight/nowhere-to-return-to-how-haaretz-told-the-story-of-gazas-destruction/0000018d-89ea-d5e7-ad8d-ebea9a320000</link><description>“仅仅在图像旁边放置文字是不够的，”记者亚登·米凯利 (Yarden Michaeli) 谈到《国土报》对加沙地带大规模破坏的交互式视觉调查时说道。 “我们真的想让人们进入故事，以产生情感影响”</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 19:39:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-08/ty-article/.highlight/nowhere-to-return-to-how-haaretz-told-the-story-of-gazas-destruction/0000018d-89ea-d5e7-ad8d-ebea9a320000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的内容 – 第 125 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-125/0000018d-89d1-d5e7-ad8d-ebf1fac20000</link><description>布林肯表示，哈马斯对停火提议的回应“显然不可能”，但美国认为“这为达成协议创造了空间” ■ 哈马斯高级官员表示，内塔尼亚胡对哈马斯的答复表明总理打算在该地区寻求冲突 ■ 几名以色列人周四，一名真主党指挥官在黎巴嫩的火箭弹和导弹袭击中受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 17:49:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-125/0000018d-89d1-d5e7-ad8d-ebf1fac20000</guid></item></channel></rss>